Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:09.92,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就宛如五條大橋的決戰一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,手握菜刀的弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:18.61,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,與手握菜刀的牛若丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.44,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,之間的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:24.88,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,改良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.76,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是香辣的味道卻讓人心蕩神馳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:32.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這種獨特的煙薰香味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.44,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是培根
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:38.36,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是複製幸平的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:40.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是用牛尾做燉牛肉才對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:42.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個培根到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:45.14,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,說到往燉牛肉裡加培根
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.42,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.92,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,用在裝飾菜裡面對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:15.65,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}比心中描繪的意象更遙遠的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:22.07,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}在一筆筆敘寫  那真實還在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}如無盡的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:31.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}來將各自的自尊心研磨透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:36.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}敞開任何言語之類的裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:45.43,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相互碰撞 相互摩擦 rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:48.10,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相遇是 shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:53.18,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}向未知的世界邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.73,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}無謀的挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:02:01.07,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}只要用手中的刀劈開明天就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.15,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}這並不是別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}是只屬於自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:12.91,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}因為我們都是未經琢磨的鑽石！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.91,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,1002)}garniture
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——————OP——————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:15.65,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}思い描いてるイメージより遙か向こう側へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:22.07,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}創り上げて行く　真実はまだ遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}果てない旅路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:31.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}お互いのプライドを研ぎ澄ませよぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:36.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}言葉なんて飾りは開けさせりやいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:45.43,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}ぶつかり合い　磨かれていく　rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:48.10,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}出會いは　shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:53.18,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}まだ知らない世界へ歩き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.73,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}無謀な挑戦者さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:02:01.07,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}手にした刃で明日を切り開けばいいんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.15,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}誰かのもんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.95,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}自分だけのストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:12.91,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}cause we are still rough diamonds on the road!
