Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:57.03,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思えだ頃の僕は今いつーごえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:59.66,shokeki_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}長い物に巻がれで
